data.description: Great 2 story home located in a gated subdivision ready to move in. Large 5 bedrooms with a great kitchen and floor plan. Master Suite offers garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet.  Bedrooms offer decent size closets and lots of storage space throughout.  Walking distance to clubhouse. Close to all amenities. Must see to appreciate! Seller will assist with buyer's closing costs with an accepted offer.
